snippet: Second-half goals from Leroy Sane and Raheem Sterling stunned Arsenal at the Etihad Stadium on Sunday as Manchester City came from behind to win 2-1 and move seven points behind leaders Chelsea....
lead_paragraph: Second-half goals from Leroy Sane and Raheem Sterling stunned Arsenal at the Etihad Stadium on Sunday as Manchester City came from behind to win 2-1 and move seven points behind leaders Chelsea.

headline.main: Manchester City See Off Arsenal With Stirring Comeback
headline.print_headline: Manchester City See Off Arsenal With Stirring Comeback
